    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1938-07-18T17:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1938-07-18T17:00:00-05:00" n="299"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d299">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">752.00114/32: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Spain</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Bowers</hi>
                    </persName>), <hi rend="italic">Then in France</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1938-07-18T18:00:00-04:00"
                            >July 18, 1938—6 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>B–446. Your 503, July 18, 1 p.m. Bay has, in the course of his recent visits to
                    Burgos in several conversations with the Franco authorities, dealt with the
                    matter of treatment of American prisoners, and it was suggested to him that
                    questions concerning prisoners be taken up by him with the authorities
                    concerned. Pursuant to this suggestion, we have therefore made our preliminary
                    approach through Bay.</p>
                <p>Until the interested American organization offered to pay expenses of
                    repatriation or exchange, it was not possible for us to make any inquiries along
                    those lines, as the Government has not appropriated funds at its disposal for
                    either of those purposes.</p>
                <p>If our preliminary approach receives favorable response, the method and details
                    of working out the repatriation or exchange can be taken up.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
